      "description": "Rate of cuckoo displacements during insert operations.\n\nDisplacements occur when cuckoo hashing must kick an existing entry to make room. High displacement rates indicate:\n\n- Load factor too high\n- Poor hash distribution\n- Potential for insert failures\n\nMaximum displacement chain: 10,000 (bounded worst-case).",
